                            <div class="yg-classic-cover-img-cont fright" data-imgurl="https://xa.yimg.com/kq/groups/3823459/homepage/name/943544.jpg?type=hr">
                                <div id="yg-classic-cover-img">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                        <div class="group-detail-sec yg-top-brdr yg-grp-sec-narrow">
                            <div class="section">
                                Group Description
                            </div>                    
                            <div class="section-row-desc">
                                <div id="ygrps-yiv-701562664">Friends, Historians, Astronomers:<br />
WELCOME!<br />
<br />
Historia Coelestis means (among other things) &quot;The Story of the Heavens&quot; in Latin.  <br />
<br />
Historia Coelestis is a discussion group and community resource for all those interested in the history of astronomy at all levels.  <br />
<br />
This group welcomes relevant contributions, questions, news and announcements including conferences and new publications, at all levels - so please do take part and contribute to the life of the group.  We all have something interesting to say, and ideas to share!<br />
<br />
Membership is open to anyone interested in our subject.  This is a friendly and informal group - however, please note that anti-social behaviour and spamming will result in banning. <br />
<br />
Stuart Williams,FRAS<br />
Moderator, Historiacoelestis<br />
Research Librarian, Society for the History of Astronomy<br />
Bloxwich, England.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                            <div class="group-detail-sec yg-top-brdr">
                                <div class="section">Group Website</div>
                                <div><a href="http://historiacoelestis.webs.com" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"> http://historiacoelestis.webs.com </a></div>
                            </div>
                        
                        <div class="group-detail-sec yg-top-brdr yg-grp-sec-narrow">
                            <div class="section">Category</div>
                            <div>Science/Astronomy</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="group-detail-sec yg-top-brdr yg-grp-sec-narrow">
                            <div class="section">
                            Group Settings
                            </div>
                            <div id="group_settings">
                             <ul >                 
                             <li><b>This is a restricted group.</b></li>
                             <li>Attachments are not permitted.</li>
                             <li>Members cannot hide email address.</li>
                             <li>Listed in Yahoo Groups directory.</li>
                            </ul>
